      "module_path": "ref_verify",
      "docs": "Secondary port for semantic review of a single (claim, evidence) reference pair. `cache_scope` routes the adapter to the correct Chain-specific capability (`ref-verifier-chain1` for Chain1, `ref-verifier-chain2` for Chain2) and prompt template (D11, CN-12). The adapter returns only `SemanticVerdict`; the usecase layer owns externally determined claim_hash/evidence_hash values and wraps the verdict into `SemanticVerifyEntry` for cache persistence. ModelTier selects fast vs final model per D5 three-tier escalation. Implemented by the `AgentRefVerifierAdapter` in infrastructure, which dispatches to the Chain-specific capability (`ref-verifier-chain1` or `ref-verifier-chain2`) per D7/D11 (CN-01).",
